<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="further-adv">further <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɜːðə(r)/    美 /'fɜːrðər/  </p>
<p>[far的比较级]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(距离、时间、程度上) 更远地；进一步地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I would be delighted to have the opportunity to discuss my application further with you.
我很高兴有机会与您进一步讨论我的申请。</p><footer>外研新选必④ – 1改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can lend you 50 dollars, but I can't go any <strong>further</strong> than that.
我可以借给你50美元,不能再多了。</p></div>

<h3 id="further-farther">辨析 further, farther</h3>
<p>两者都为far的比较级，但是farther只用于本义“(空间距离上的) 更远”。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Africa is further / farther from England than France.
非洲距离英国比距离法国远。</p></div></div>